# Backend (.NET)

- Target: .NET 8+
- API: Clean Architecture, DI, EF Core for MSSQL
- Migrations: `dotnet ef migrations add` from the API project directory
- Functions: C# isolated worker or in-process per existing project style
- Configuration: see `docs/configuration.md` — `appsettings.json` for local defaults; secrets in `api.env`/user secrets; Azure App Configuration when `AZURE_APP_CONFIG` is set

## Commands (from repo root, after import)
```bash
dotnet build dertinfo.sln
dotnet test dertinfo.sln
```
